The tragedy comes as US President Donald Trump has pledged to deport millions of undocumented migrants living in America. JOHANNESBURG A Mexican man who was deported from the United States has killed himself, jumping off a bridge in view of the US border.The 44-year-old threw himself to his death on Tuesday. He jumped 30 metres. Witnesses say he was in great distress after being sent back to Mexico for a third time.The tragedy comes as US President Donald Trump has pledged to deport millions of undocumented migrants living in America.He s called Mexican migrants criminals and pledged to build a massive border wall.